WEBVTT

00:00:00.746 --> 00:00:03.373
Leo ninataka kuzungumza nawe kuhusu ndoto.

00:00:03.999 --> 00:00:06.716
nimekuwa mwota ndoto mzuri maisha yote,

00:00:06.740 --> 00:00:08.716
na ni nzuri kuliko za kwenye filamu.

00:00:08.740 --> 00:00:10.683
(kicheko)

00:00:10.707 --> 00:00:13.415
zaidi ya kupaa, kupumua moto,

00:00:13.439 --> 00:00:16.280
na kufanya wanaume wazuri 
watokee kwa ghafla ...

00:00:16.304 --> 00:00:18.281
(kicheko)

00:00:18.305 --> 00:00:20.713
Ninaweza kufanya vitu kama kusoma na
kuandika muziki.

00:00:21.344 --> 00:00:24.675
Cha kufurahisha ni kuwa niliandika
habari yangu binafsi kwenda chuoni

00:00:24.699 --> 00:00:26.019
nikiwa kwenye ndoto.

00:00:26.043 --> 00:00:28.798
Na nilikubaliwa. Hivyo sawa.

00:00:29.873 --> 00:00:31.679
Ninafikiri kwa namna ya picha.